column3: I'm working to improve the strains of fruit we grow. There's nothing like a sweet and succulent morsel to lift the people's spirits.
Captain! I'll do my utmost to bring pride to the name of the...ahem, Samiel Search Squad!
Please accept my apologies again for the trouble I caused. I promise not to go running off again, and focus instead on doing what I do best─analyzing specimens.
Yalana puts on a show of displeasure when the chief comes around with a request, but it's mainly to keep up appearances. She actually relishes the work.
